Package org.buildmlearn.appstore.models

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AppInfo
    Model class of the App, currently used for installed apps, rendered from the BuildmLearn file of the apps.
    Apps
    Model class of the app, currently used for store apps, rendered from the Store XML.
    Card
    Template model for Flash cards type of apps.
    CategoriesCard
    Template model for Categories
    FlashModel
    Template model for the FlashCard type of apps.
    InfoModel
    Template model for Info-Type of apps.
    Question
    Template model for Quiz type of apps.
    QuizModel
    Template model for Quiz type of apps
    SpellingsModel
    Template model for Spellings Puzzle type of apps.
    WordModel
    Template class for the words for the Spellings puzzle apps.
